item.title: Johnny Cash - The Mercy Seat - Key of Am - BruderMaister
item.description: Play along video for the song The Mercy Seat by Johnny Cash from the channel BruderMaister. Chords used in the song: Am, Am7, Ammaj7, B♭, E, Fmaj7, G, Gm.

item.title: The Beatles - Something - Ukulele Cheats
